Document: XRVRS
Path: godot/classes/class_xrvrs.rst
Summary: The make_vrs_texture method generates a VRS texture with specified target size and eye focus points.

Method: make_vrs_texture(target_size: Vector2, eye_foci: PackedVector2Array) → RID  
Creates a VRS texture using the provided target size (Vector2) and eye focus points (PackedVector2Array). The method returns an RID reference to the generated texture.
